    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab eius
                        nativitate millesimo centesimo octuagesimo quarto, septimo kalendas
                        septembris, indictione secunda. Manifesti sumus nos <persName
                            ref="#people/3226">Castracane</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3214">Uberti</persName>
                        <persName ref="#people/3216">Sesmondi</persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3227">Gangalande</placeName> et <persName><name ref="Willa"
                                >Guilia</name></persName> eius uxor et filia <persName><name
                                ref="Iaffer">Iafferis</name></persName> (…) interveniente mihi
                        notitia <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Rodelandus"
                            >Rolandi</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Guarmignanus">Guarminiani</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> domini imperatoris (…) per hanc cartulam
                        vendimus et tradimus tibi iamdicto Rolando iudici recipienti procuratorio
                        nomine ad partem <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                                key="#Hospitals">Altopascio</placeName></orgName> pro ipso hospitale
                        unam videlicet petiam de terra que est campus in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210" key="#Roads">Pothi ubi dicitur alle
                        Prata</placeName>. Et tenet unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>,
                        alterum in terra <persName><name ref="Gherardinus"
                            >Gerardini</name></persName>, latera vero ambo in terris suprascripti
                        hospitalis. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: dupli (…) et lib. decem argenti optimi,
                        consulum quoque et treguanorum lucensium et lucensis potestatis presentium
                        et futurorum. (…) Actum in loco <placeName ref="#places/3235"
                            >Canova</placeName> prope <placeName ref="#places/3234"
                            >Rosarolum</placeName>. (…) <rs key="#Witness">Testes</rs> ad hoc vocati
                        sunt <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Borgognone"
                            >Burgognone</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Pungilio"
                                >Pungilionis</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Widoctus">Guidoctus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Widuccius">Guiducius</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Maginectus">Mainectus</name></persName>
                        germani quondam *** qui rogati testes interfuerunt. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Bartholomaeus"
                            >Bartholomeus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris post traditam
                        complevi atque dedi. </ab>
